snippet.title: Exoprimal Season 2 Trailer + Street Fighter Colab | TGS Trailer 2023
snippet.description: Check out gameplay from Exoprimal's upcoming second season, which features a variety of wild emotes and a Street Fighter crossover event (including a high-kicking Chun-Li mech), launching on Xbox and Game Pass on October 18.
